      "text": "うう……これじゃみんなバラバラです……\n悪い意味で、今までにないステージになっちゃいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh… The new group is a complete mess.\nIt’s going to be a performance like no other—but not in a good way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
