      "text": "高い目標を掲げるのはいいことだ\nでも、そのせいで自分を見失ったら意味がない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s good to set high goals.\nBut they’re meaningless if you lose sight of yourself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_03-kkr019.m4a",
      "text": "私、自分を……見失ってる……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m losing… sight of myself?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
