      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈や莉央さんを目標にするのもいい\nでも彼女達だって完璧じゃない。失敗だってするよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s fine to hold up Mana and Rio-san as your targets.\nBut they aren’t perfect either. They’ve screwed up too.",
