      "text": "（そう、麻奈さんは凄いアイドルで、目標）\n（……けど、私は私。赤崎こころ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Mana-san is an incredible idol and still my goal in life.)\n(But I’m me. Kokoro Akazaki. No one else.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 297.8666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
